{"tid":1451906,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【教徒與你同行】覺得憤怒，痛心，無力嘅同我全部入嚟","createTime":"2019-08-11T21:47:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T22:15:58.000Z","uid":296674,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4d5453468c5ea38f86f0ed56de02e52fa6d269ce","tid":1451906,"uid":296674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T21:47:56.000Z","msg":"經過 721，65，811，相信大家同我一樣<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">覺得林鄭呢個自稱「教徒」埋沒良心，視人命如草芥<br />\n覺得黑警濫權違反公義，道德，良知<br />\n覺得高牆之下嘅雞蛋，就算點樣勇武，不斷進化都好，對著真槍實彈headshot即刻一命嗚呼<br />\n覺得夜晚好難瞓覺，好多煩惱纏身<br />\n覺得自己好無用，連係人係鬼到分唔到，保護唔到一班手足<br />\n覺得香港只要一輸，就會無得翻身</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我喺外國，撫心自問能夠做嘅好有限；不過同教會牧師傾過，佢覺得大家可以試下祈禱<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">人人都可以祈禱</span></span><br />\n信徒得，和理非得，著住full gear都得<br />\n喺屋企，喺地鐵站，係戰場上都得<br />\n只要你肯誠心祈禱，神一定會聽<br />\n<br />\n呢句經文係商台DJ Leo Ball post 喺facebook post嘅,就當係今日嘅經文啦：<br />\n<blockquote>「各位親愛的，不要自己伸冤，寧可給主的憤怒留地步，因為經上記著：「主說：『伸冤在我，我必報應。』」」羅馬書‬ ‭12:19‬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n新手可以試下咁樣祈禱：<br />\n你同上帝講，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">希望佢伸張正義  求佢俾你有分辨善惡嘅心  唔好比仇恨遮蔽（記唔記得梁天琦獄中家書呀）</span></span><br />\n就係咁多  一句搞掂  你有更多嘢想講嘅  無任歡迎  神一定會聽<br />\n<br />\n祈禱之後有冇即刻嘅果效我唔知  食藥都唔會即刻醫到病啦<br />\n但係我見到<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">南非廢除種族隔離  柏林圍牆倒下  美國成功爭取種族平權</span></span><br />\n我覺得長遠嚟講  <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">企喺正義一邊嘅 做神喜悅嘅事嘅 一定會贏  仲會用出人意表嘅方法贏到開巷</span></span><br />\n<br />\n依家最緊要嘅就係頭腦清醒  準備打長期戰爭  保持希望  <br />\n希望你祈禱之後 內心有少少平安 然後繼續上路 一個手足都唔少得<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n香港人加油</span></span>"},{"pid":"ec7b518cbc37e48222dc8021f0e86348c4ffaf75","tid":1451906,"uid":296674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T21:48:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5da8fa86aa479574fc8a0ab14a70d2faa42e7d6b","tid":1451906,"uid":296674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T21:48:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5c29b4d5a424a9ec00b8a7abb5e1097e57e5bd19","tid":1451906,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T21:48:27.000Z","msg":"耶穌愛你"},{"pid":"35a4aed854535ac9ca148df9d1d2c797293257d9","tid":1451906,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T21:48:38.000Z","msg":"與神同行"},{"pid":"a4d779a12c4961a02874fbe57a13ba2f2df281d2","tid":1451906,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T21:49:05.000Z","msg":"連教會都用催淚彈 黑警可恥"},{"pid":"6ebb291fcbce16384a6d08662662e03d6c4d90db","tid":1451906,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T21:50:00.000Z","msg":"一班教徒每個禮拜六都遊行 因為佢地擇善固執 唔會放棄任何人"},{"pid":"5319763ba39aa6b7fde6979416fefe9bb2966453","tid":1451906,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T21:50:14.000Z","msg":"We Connect"},{"pid":"58b9a8fbec1ff764da72ac77cefd0f115bdffcc5","tid":1451906,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T21:50:35.000Z","msg":"Sing Hallellujah to the LORD"},{"pid":"029746876eb8faa799413124bab627b72b410d52","tid":1451906,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T21:50:49.000Z","msg":"Sing Hallellujah to the LORD"},{"pid":"bcdcf9efd268a27e104a73b5abe489ac19d7bfff","tid":1451906,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T21:51:13.000Z","msg":"GOD is POWER"},{"pid":"4a1d0de57aabcc3506d995bbebcfa67d545edd29","tid":1451906,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T21:51:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"576729a1c50ef0333d7172ee709821c94b03ed64","tid":1451906,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T21:54:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3edbd8019261d4fd0c0a8cac41f1640e8061fc23","tid":1451906,"uid":296674,"like":